@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor "Manager" as User
participant "AdminDashboard\n(JS class)" as Dashboard
participant "ApiService\n(JS class)" as ApiService
participant "JwtAuthFilter" as JwtFilter
participant "ManagerController" as Controller
participant "RevenueServiceImpl" as Service
participant "IBookingRepository" as Repo

User -> Dashboard: 1. Vào tab "Xem tổng doanh thu"
Dashboard -> ApiService: 2. loadRevenueData('week')
ApiService -> JwtFilter: 3. GET /api/manager/revenue?period=week\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>
JwtFilter -> JwtFilter: 4. validateToken() + extractRole()\nset SecurityContext (ROLE_MANAGER)
JwtFilter -> Controller: 5. Chuyển request
Controller -> Service: 6. getRevenue("week")
Service -> Service: 7. getFromDate("week") → now - 7 ngày
Service -> Repo: 8. findByBookingDateBetweenAndStatus(from, to, "confirmed")
Repo --> Service: 9. List<Booking>
Service -> Service: 10. Tính totalRevenue, totalBookings\nbookedRoomsCount, avgDailyRevenue\ngroup theo ngày → chartData
Service --> Controller: 11. RevenueResponse
Controller --> ApiService: 12. 200 OK + JSON
ApiService --> Dashboard: 13. data
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 14. Cập nhật stat cards
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 15. renderChart(labels, values, 'week')
Dashboard --> User: 16. Hiển thị biểu đồ + stats

User -> Dashboard: 17. Click filter "Tháng này"
Dashboard -> ApiService: 18. loadRevenueData('month')
ApiService -> Controller: 19. GET /api/manager/revenue?period=month
Controller -> Service: 20. getRevenue("month")
Service -> Repo: 21. findByBookingDateBetweenAndStatus(from, to, "confirmed")
Repo --> Service: 22. List<Booking>
Service --> Controller: 23. RevenueResponse
Controller --> ApiService: 24. 200 OK + JSON
ApiService --> Dashboard: 25. data mới
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 26. revenueChartInstance.destroy()
Dashboard -> Dashboard: 27. renderChart() lại
Dashboard --> User: 28. Cập nhật biểu đồ + stats
@enduml